  "markup": "Once in awhile you run into a case that just does not want to respond. Maybe a persistent hip pain patient or a TMD case that will not resolve. \u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nEver wondered if a set of Laser Probes might be useful, or you may have a set of probes and are not sure how to get the most out of them. Then this is the webinar for you. \u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nJoin Dr. Chris Carraway, and our Special Guest Speaker Dr. Brian Sherwood of Australia, for a host of tips and tricks for better outcomes, that we call \u0022Clinical Pearls.\u0022\u003Cbr /\u003E\n\u003Cbr /\u003E\nThere should be a lot of take-home value to be had by attending this one."
}]]></Value>
